OL,3,CMps and councillors react to local
OL,4,Celections being postponed until 2026
OL,6,FSome councils in the South and South
OL,7,FEast of England have been successful
OL,8,Fin their bids to be on the
OL,9,Fgovernment's fast-track devolution
OL,10,Fprogramme.
OL,12,FLocal elections will be postponed by a
OL,13,Fyear in Essex, Sussex, Surrey and
OL,14,FHampshire, ministers have confirmed.
OL,16,FThe affected areas are East Sussex,
OL,17,FWest Sussex, Essex, Thurrock,
OL,18,FHampshire, the Isle of Wight, and
OL,19,FSurrey.
