OL,3,CMps and councillors react to local
OL,4,Celections being postponed until 2026
OL,6,FIt will pave the way for directly-
OL,7,Felected mayors for Greater Essex,
OL,8,FHampshire & Solent, and Sussex &
OL,9,FBrighton.
OL,11,FThe decision to postpone council
OL,12,Felections, due to take place in May
OL,13,Fand now to be held in 2026, has been
OL,14,Fdeeply controversial.
OL,16,FConservative MP for Arundel and South
OL,17,FDowns, Andrew Griffith, has described
OL,18,Fit as "an outrageous decision" and
OL,19,F"democratic larceny".
