OL,4,Celections being postponed until 2026
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Labour's Bella Sankey,
OL,7,Fleader of Brighton & Hove City
OL,8,FCouncil, described the announcement as
OL,9,F"an historic and exciting moment for
OL,10,Four region".
OL,12,FLib Dem leader Sir Ed Davey said: "The
OL,13,FLiberal Democrats made sweeping gains
OL,14,Fagainst the Conservatives at the
OL,15,FGeneral Election, and now failing Tory-
OL,16,Frun councils are running scared and
OL,17,Fdenying voters a chance to kick them
OL,18,Fout of office in May."
