OL,3,CMps and councillors react to local
OL,4,Celections being postponed until 2026
OL,6,FThe Conservative leader of Kent County
OL,7,FCouncil, Roger Gough, said: "I am
OL,8,Fastonished and bitterly disappointed
OL,9,Fthat residents and businesses of Kent
OL,10,Fhave been let down by the government
OL,11,Fand will not be able to benefit from
OL,12,Fthe increased monies, powers and
OL,13,Fopportunities promised through
OL,14,Fdevolution."
OL,16,FAs part of the changes, the government
OL,17,Fhas written to all councils with two-
OL,18,Ftiers, to ask them to put forward
OL,19,Fplans to create larger unitary
OL,20,Fauthorities.
